CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 15, 1962, pg. 17 reads: "Beautiful Yard Awards Program - Cultivators of above-average yards in Homewood attended the seventh annual awards program and tea sponsored by the Homewood Community Improvement Association. Pictured in the photo at the upper left are Mrs. John Koshan and Mrs. Clem Blackwell (third and fourth from left) accepting awards from Mrs. Robert L. Vann and James V. Cunningham of ACTION-Housing, Inc....-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait James V. Cunningham and Jessie Vann, presenting awards to Mrs. John Koshan and Mrs. Clem Blackwell, posed in Bethesda United Presbyterian Church during seventh annual beautiful yard awards program
